$interpreted: : Three years later...
Yan-Bo: Karnulla?
Karnulla: Grandpa Yan-Bo, good morning!
Yan-Bo: Ahhh, yes. Good morning〜Today's homework, you have done?
Karnulla: Of course! As soon as the sun rose I did my sweeping, meditation, training,
Karnulla: and told myself the ten good things I'll do today.
Yan-Bo: A good child, you are. Please, fruits for breakfast, you shall gather.
Karnulla: Grandpa Yan-Bo......I haven't had acorn shells in a while......
Yan-Bo: Wait for you to finish picking fruit, I will. Then the shells off the Awful Acorns back, I will scare. The shells, I will bring them back home for you to eat, yes.
Karnulla: I kinda think...I'm just so big now, I think I'll be able to scare them out of their shells——
Yan-Bo: ——NO!
Yan-Bo: If strike the Awful Acorns to death you do, then murder this will be!
Karnulla: But, but...I can already control my power...
Yan-Bo: No means no! Argue with you I will not. Go pick the fruit, you shall!
Yan-Bo: Hmm......At ease, I am not. Go follow him, I shall.
Karnulla: Ooo, what a delicious smell. What is it?
Veteran Hunger: A frogodile!?
Rookie Hunter: What...what should I do??
Karnulla: Relax, I won't hurt you. Grandpa Yan-Bo said I must be kind to everybody.
Karnulla: What are you baking? It smells so good!
Rookie Hunter: This is a fish we caught. You've never eaten one?
Karnulla: A dead fish! You eat meat?
Veteran Hunger: It's just food. No need to make a fuss.
Rookie Hunter: Take a bite! It's really good〜
Karnulla: Hmm......It seems so delicious. Just one bite won't matter, right?
Karnulla: What are you doing!? Grandpa Yan-Bo said you can't use violence!
Veteran Hunger: Hey, we've found ourselves an idiot frogodile. We've hit jackpot!
Rookie Hunter: Kill him quick and skin him. We'll make a bundle!
Yan-Bo: Picking on Karnulla, are you? Teach you a lesson, I will!
Karnulla: Thank you, Grandpa Yan-Bo......
Yan-Bo: Karnulla, disappointed in you I am!
Karnulla: Huh? I listened to what you said. I didn't use any violence......
Yan-Bo: Fish you have eaten. This I have seen. Do not destroy life, I have taught you not?
Karnulla: But I didn't kill it. They said it's just food......
Yan-Bo: Excuses! To home, you shall go!
Yan-Bo: Trigger his violent nature, will this event?
Yan-Bo: A more strict education I must use. Away from evil, I must take Karnulla. To virtue, I shall lead him......
